
You can run this test in MOBILE, TABLET, DESKTOP view be setting the required vied from the page spec in the pageobject package.
 as below set to one of  :
 MOBILE, TABLET, DESKTOP


 let selectedDevice= DESKTOP_VIEW;


 by default this test is run in chromedriver server
 for cross browser testing in firefox, chrome and Michrosoft Edge plead go the the wdio confi file amd at search for serves and un comment for selenium-standalone server
 as below:

    services: ["chromedriver"],
    //services: ["selenium-standalone"],

    When run with selenium server plase quit the server befor run again.


    to run this test run from the commandline:
    npm run test

    OR
     npx wdio wdio.conf.js